{"data": [{"id": "4743656", "title": "SWBI: Time To Double Down On Guns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rodeo Competition\" data-id=\"956210960\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ferrantraite</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Ahead of the election, we published an article on Smith &amp; Wesson Brands (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SWBI\" title=\"Smith &amp; Wesson Brands, Inc.\">SWBI</a>), linked below.</p> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725712-swbi-the-upcoming-election-is-the-ultimate-catalyst\">Smith &amp; Wesson Brands Stock: The Upcoming Election Is The Ultimate Catalyst (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SWBI\" title=\"Smith &amp; Wesson Brands, Inc.\">SWBI</a></span>) </a><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725712-swbi-the-upcoming-election-is-the-ultimate-catalyst\">| Seeking Alpha</a></p> <p>The thesis of the article was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743656-swbi-time-to-double-down-on-guns", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 21:56:54"}, {"id": "4743653", "title": "Wingstop: Flying Too Close To The Sun On Icarian Wings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Engraving of death of Icarus\" data-id=\"92822107\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1504px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Photos.com</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Cruise Flight: A Fast-Casual Flying Too High</h2> <p>Like a <a href=\"https://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/Visit/Museum-Exhibits/Fact-Sheets/Display/Article/196280/lockheed-p-38l-lightning/\" rel=\"noopener\">Lockheed P-38 Lightning</a> in the 40s, Wingstop Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WING\" title=\"Wingstop Inc.\">WING</a></span>) has soared above the already lofty heights of today\u2019s fast-casual restaurants. Last quarter marked the 21st consecutive quarter of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/92822107/image_92822107.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743653-wingstop-flying-too-close-to-the-sun-on-icarian-wings", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 21:54:48"}, {"id": "4743651", "title": "WillScot Holdings: Under The Radar Roll-Up With Attractive Unit Economics", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sunset over the Racetrack\" data-id=\"2175923913\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://st