cker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a></span>), the company reported an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4153317-micron-surges-q4-results-guidance-ai-demand\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4153317-micron-surges-q4-results-guidance-ai-demand\" target=\"_blank\">excellent earnings</a> announcement. In the previous quarter, Micron earned $1.18 in EPS, clocking in $7.75B in revenues, a 93.3% YoY gain. Micron surpassed the consensus estimates by 7 cents and $110M. In addition to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2009686025/image_2009686025.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743643-micron-a-solid-buy-into-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 21:13:13"}, {"id": "4743660", "title": "TUI AG 2024 Q4 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by TUI AG in conjunction with their 2024 Q4 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106120\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743660-tui-ag-2024-q4-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 21:08:20"}, {"id": "4743639", "title": "Bank of America Is A 'Buy' Despite Seeming Overvaluation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173572523/image_173572523.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Outside view of a bank with American flag\" data-id=\"173572523\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3770px\" height=\"2582px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173572523/image_173572523.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173572523/image_173572523.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173572523/image