g ones. However, the unrealized profit was way higher at the beginning of the year, as the stock peaked at \u20ac178 and has</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808243985/image_1808243985.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743633-be-semiconductor-a-market-leader-with-enormous-dividend-growth-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 20:46:36"}]}